h Lord of Balwearie35岁，母亲Lady Isobel de Warren40岁。他与Elizabeth Harborne在英国英格兰米德萊可維斯特明斯特聖 克萊門特 丹妮絲结婚。他们至少是1个儿子和1个女儿的父母。他去世于1406年在英国苏格兰費伏吉卡爾迪享年56岁。"},"hr":{"1350–1406":"1350.–1406.","1360–1454":"1360–1454","1350–1424":"1350.–1424","1375–1440":"1375–1440","1389–1424":"1389.–1424","1315–1355":"1315–1355.","1310–Female":"1310–preminula","1440":"1440","1340":"1340.","1350":"1350.","1360":"1360","1315":"1315","1424":"1424","1389":"1389.","1355":"1355.","1454":"1454","Abt 1375":"oko 1375.","1310":"1310","1375":"1375","1406":"1406.","Balwearie Castle, Fife, Scotland":"Fife, Škotska, United Kingdom","Balwearie Castle, Kirkcaldy, Fifeshire, Scotland":"Kirkcaldy, Fife, Škotska, United Kingdom","Kirkcaldy, Fife, Scotland":"Kirkcaldy, Fife, Scotland","St Clement Danes,Westminster,Middlesex,England":"St Clement Danes, Westminster, Middlesex, Engleska, United Kingdom","Balweary, Fife, Scotland":"Fife, Škotska, United Kingdom","Brabourne, Kent, England":"Brabourne, Kent, England"},"cs":{"1350–1406":"1350–1406","1360–1454":"1360–1454","1350–1424":"1350–1424","1375–1440":"1375–1440","1389–1424":"1389–1424","1315–1355":"1315–1355","1310–Female":"1310–Zesnulá","1440":"1440","1340":"1340","1350":"1350","1360":"1360","1315":"1315","1424":"1424","1389":"1389","1355":"1355","1454":"1454","Abt 1375":"okolo 1375","1310":"1310","1375":"1375","1406":"1406","Balwearie Castle, Fife, Scotland":"Fife, Skotsko, United Kingdom","Balwearie Castle, Kirkcaldy, Fifeshire, Scotland":"Kirkcaldy, Fife, Skotsko, United Kingdom","Kirkcaldy, Fife, Scotland":"Kirkcaldy, Fife, Scotland","St Clement Danes,Westminster,Middlesex,England":"St Clement Danes, Westminster, Middlesex, Anglie, United Kingdom","Balweary, Fife, Scotland":"Fife, Skotsko, United Kingdom","Brabourne, Kent, England":"Brabourne, Kent, Anglie"},"da":{"1350–1406":"1350–1406","1360–1454":"1360–1454","1350–1424":"1350–1424","1375–1440":"1375–1440","1389–1424":"1389–1424","1315–1355":"1315–1355","1310–Female":"1310–Afdød","1440":"1440","1340":"1340",